title: President Donald J. Trump Announces Presidential Delegation to Commemorate the 15th Anniversary of Timor-Leste Independence and Attend the Presidential Inauguration of His Excellency Francisco Guterres â€“ The White House
content:
Nominations & Appointments			
Issued on:
May 10, 2017
President Donald J. Trump today announced the designation of a Presidential Delegation to commemorate the 15th anniversary of Timor-Leste independence and to attend the Presidential Inauguration of His Excellency Francisco Guterres on May 20, 2017.The Honorable Karen C. Stanton, United States Ambassador to the Democratic Republic of Timor-Leste, will lead the delegation.Members of the Presidential Delegation:Mr. W. Patrick Murphy, Deputy Assistant Secretary of State for Southeast Asia.
